msgstr ""
"Project-Id-Version: Yakuza 6 Translation\n"
"Last-Translator: SavT\n"
"MIME-Version: 1.0\n"
"Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8\n"
"Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit\n"
"Language: it\n"

msgctxt "0||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1||||4"
msgid "What in the world is this?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3||||4"
msgid "Wh-What the hell!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4||||4"
msgid "Ah, so that's where Michio-kun's head is.\r\nFinally found you!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5||||4"
msgid "What was that lazy brat thinking,\r\nleaving something as special as you out here?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||||4"
msgid "Hey, what is that thing?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7||||4"
msgid "Oh, sorry. I hope it didn't scare you too much."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8||||4"
msgid "This little guy is the head of\r\nour stunning Ono Michio-kun."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9||||4"
msgid "Ono Michio-kun...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "10||||4"
msgid "Yup! He's an original mascot we're trying to\r\npromote as the sparkling new face of Onomichi!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11||||4"
msgid "A mascot...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12||||4"
msgid "Huh? Do you not know what those are?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "13||||4"
msgid "Well, sort of. Aren't they those cute character\r\nthings that have been popping up recently?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14||||4"
msgid "Precisely! These days, they're most commonly\r\nused as PR to boost local tourism and culture."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "15||||4"
msgid "I'm in a real bind here, though.\r\nMy usual actor's flown the coop."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "16||||4"
msgid "You have an actor?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17||||4"
msgid "Of course. A part-timer who donned the guise of\r\nMichio-kun to spread cheer to the world."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "18||||4"
msgid "All I did was give him a few pointers.\r\nKids these days can't take a little criticism."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "19||||4"
msgid "Huh..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "20||||4"
msgid "But honestly, we have a big event coming up.\r\nMichio-kun's supposed to make a dazzling appearance."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "21||||4"
msgid "What a mess...\r\nI'm in hot water without an actor."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "22||||4"
msgid "Why don't you do it yourself?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "23||||4"
msgid "No no, I'm all about management.\r\nI can't act and run the event at the same time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "24||||4"
msgid "Michio-kun's pretty darn big for one of these\r\nmascots, too. Heavy doesn't begin to describe it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||||4"
msgid "I need my actor to be tall and muscular. A wimpy guy\r\nlike me would never last the whole event."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "26||||4"
msgid "But where could I possibly find someone big and\r\nstrong enough to handle the role? What a pickle..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "27||||4"
msgid "Hm...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||||4"
msgid "Hm..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "29||||4"
msgid "Hmmm!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||||4"
msgid "I don't like where this is going."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "31||||4"
msgid "I found one!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "32||||4"
msgid "I'm not getting in that thing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "33||||4"
msgid "Come on, please!\r\nI'll make it up to you somehow!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "34||||4"
msgid "Michio-kun needs someone like you. You're big,\r\nyou're strong, and you have tons of time on your hands!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||||4"
msgid "This really isn't my style."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||||4"
msgid "I'm begging you!\r\nI'll do whatever it takes to get you in there!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "37||||4"
msgid "Besides, there are countless precious little children\r\nwaiting for Michio-kun's performance."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "38||||4"
msgid "Think of their smiling faces.\r\nYou don't want to leave them disappointed, do you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "39||||4"
msgid "Hm..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "40||||4"
msgid "Please help me!\r\nYou need to protect their innocent smiles!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||||4"
msgid "I'm not really interested in being a mascot...\r\nWhat should I do?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||||4"
msgid "Let me think about it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||||4"
msgid "Okay! I'll be waiting right in\r\nthis very spot until you're ready!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||||4"
msgid "All right, I'll do it.\r\nJust for a bit."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||||4"
msgid "Thank you so much, Michio-kun!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||||4"
msgid "Hey, I'm not Michio yet. The name's Kiryu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "47||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san! I'm the producer for this event, Hironaka.\r\nWe're gonna make a great team!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "48||||4"
msgid "Now let's get moving! The sooner we make you\r\ninto Ono Michio-kun, the better! Come on!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "49||||4"
msgid "Urgh..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||||4"
msgid "Won't you please be my mascot actor?\r\nI'm begging you!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "51||||4"
msgid "Oooh, it's perfect! You're a great fit!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "52||||4"
msgid "Hey, do I really have to go through with this?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "53||||4"
msgid "Don't sound so hesitant! It'll be impossible\r\nto find someone else who suits it so well!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "54||||4"
msgid "It's heavy, though. And hot. And hard to breathe in.\r\nI can see why your old actor ran off."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||||4"
msgid "Cheer up, guy. Ono Michio-kun is the new symbol\r\nof Onomichi! He's like an idol for these people!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||||4"
msgid "What does any of this have to do with Onomichi, anyway?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||||4"
msgid "Huh!? You can't tell?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||||4"
msgid "First up is his charming face, carefully modeled off\r\nthe local town of Setouchi's specialty hassaku orange!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "59||||4"
msgid "On top of that rests a steamy hat based on\r\nOnomichi's traditional food, Onomichi ramen!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||||4"
msgid "Around his waist we have a deliciously fishy pouch\r\nto show how much this town adores its seafood!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||||4"
msgid "And on his feet, cool rubber boots serve\r\nas a sign of our community's fisherman roots!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||||4"
msgid "Finally, Ono Michio-kun's shirt has his name, O-N-O,\r\nemblazoned on the front in big, bold letters!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||||4"
msgid "He's a great representation of our town's beauty.\r\nDon't you think he's just the perfect little mascot?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||||4"
msgid "I don't think I'd go that far..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||||4"
msgid "Either way, just be confident! You look amazing,\r\nKiryu-san! Or should I say, Michio-kun!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||||4"
msgid "So, what do you need me to do?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "67||||4"
msgid "Oh yeah. The kids will be showing up soon,\r\nso let's start with a performance! Make it fun for them!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||||4"
msgid "But, whatever you do, don't under any\r\ncircumstances break character!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "69||||4"
msgid "And what character is that?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "70||||4"
msgid "Ono Michio-kun is an Onomichi-based fisherman who\r\nloves the ocean, so he should be as refined as possible."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "71||||4"
msgid "This face, refined?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72||||4"
msgid "As for your speech mannerisms, you'll need to\r\nuse \"michi\" in your greetings when you can."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "73||||4"
msgid "Michi?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "74||||4"
msgid "\"Hello-michi!\" or \"Nice to michi!\"\r\nThings like that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "75||||4"
msgid "Let's give it a little test drive.\r\nNice to michi! And, go!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "76||||4"
msgid "Nice to michi..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "77||||4"
msgid "You're getting the hang of it now!\r\nJust give it some more energy for the event, okay?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "78||||4"
msgid "Next is... the delightful catchphrase\r\nwe have for when you find yourself in trouble."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "79||||4"
msgid "In those situations, just say \"Oh no!\""
msgstr ""

msgctxt "80||||4"
msgid "Another round of practice! Ready, and..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||||4"
msgid "Oh no..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "82||||4"
msgid "Excellent! By the by, the English phrase \"oh no\"\r\nsounds just like the Ono of your name. Cool, huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "83||||4"
msgid "I can't imagine anyone who'd think that's cool..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84||||4"
msgid "One more thing! This is the last one!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "85||||4"
msgid "There's still more? What now...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "86||||4"
msgid "Ono Michio-kun's charismatic pose!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "87||||4"
msgid "I have to pose?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "88||||4"
msgid "Ono..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "89||||4"
msgid "Michio!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "91||||4"
msgid "Just follow my example!\r\nIt's mostly for when you arrive at and leave events."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "92||||4"
msgid "This really isn't for me..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "93||||4"
msgid "Come on, don't be such a downer!\r\nJust think of the children!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||||4"
msgid "Your turn! Here we go!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "95||||4"
msgid "Ono..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "96||||4"
msgid "Michio!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "97||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san... That was impeccable!\r\nThere's no doubt. You've really become Ono Michio!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "98||||4"
msgid "Well that's upsetting..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||||4"
msgid "Oh! The kids should be just about here!\r\nYou can do it, big guy. Just give it your all!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "100||||4"
msgid "There aren't many rules beyond what I told you,\r\nso just try to relax and you'll be okay!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||||4"
msgid "You're cutting me loose, huh?\r\nAnything could happen, you know."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "102||||4"
msgid "It'll be fine! You're Ono Michio, Kiryu-san!\r\nAh, here they are! Go for the gold!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||||4"
msgid "Whoa, it's Ono Michio!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "104||||4"
msgid "You're right! It's really him!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||||4"
msgid "I'm so happy he's here! Yay, Ono Michio-kun!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "106||||4"
msgid "I guess this thing is more popular than I thought.\r\nWell, here goes nothing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "107||||4"
msgid "Hi. I'm Ono Michio."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "108||||4"
msgid "......"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "109||||4"
msgid "......"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "110||||4"
msgid "......"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "111||||4"
msgid "Looks like I need to put a little more energy into it.\r\nNot much choice now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "112||||4"
msgid "Hiya, kiddos! It's me!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "113||||4"
msgid "With my charming hassaku face!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "114||||4"
msgid "Steamy Onomichi ramen hat!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||||4"
msgid "Cute fish pouch!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "116||||4"
msgid "Cool boots, vital for any fisherman!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "117||||4"
msgid "And my bold and trendy Ono shirt!\r\nThat's right, I'm the pride of Onomichi..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "118||||4"
msgid "Ono..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "119||||4"
msgid "Michio!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "120||||4"
msgid "......"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "121||||4"
msgid "......"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "122||||4"
msgid "......"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "123||||4"
msgid "If it's fun you want... then bring it on!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||||4"
msgid "Man oh man! He's so cool!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "125||||4"
msgid "I'm in love!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||||4"
msgid "His voice is amazing!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "127||||4"
msgid "It's all in a day's work."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "128||||4"
msgid "All right. I hope you kiddos are ready to play.\r\nNow then!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "129||||4"
msgid "Nice to meet you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "130||||4"
msgid "Huh? Nice to meet you...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "131||||4"
msgid "R-Right, I remember now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "132||||4"
msgid "Nice to michi!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "133||||4"
msgid "Yay! Nice to michi!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "134||||4"
msgid "Nice to michi!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "135||||4"
msgid "Nice to michi!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "136||||4"
msgid "What a mess.\r\nThis mascot stuff really takes it out of you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "138||||4"
msgid "Michio-kun! Take this!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "139||||4"
msgid "Blam! Pow! Biff! Zap!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "140||||4"
msgid "Take this, and this!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||||4"
msgid "These little..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "143||||4"
msgid "You brats are gonna pay for this!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "145||||4"
msgid "I'm so scared... Why won't he say \"oh no\"?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "146||||4"
msgid "So that's what they wanted... Sorry about that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "147||||4"
msgid "Oh no!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "148||||4"
msgid "Yippee! He said it, he really said it!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "149||||4"
msgid "Oh no! Oh no!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "150||||4"
msgid "Aha. That's what they were after all along.\r\nI should have realized sooner."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "151||||4"
msgid "C'mon! Let's play, Michio-kun!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "153||||4"
msgid "Michio-kun! It's time for the main event!\r\nYour talk show awaits!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "154||||4"
msgid "Talk show...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "155||||4"
msgid "Yup, you heard me! This is your big moment!\r\nNow scoot on over here!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "156||||4"
msgid "A-All right..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "157||||4"
msgid "Hello there everyone!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "158||||4"
msgid "Hi!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "159||||4"
msgid "Hi!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "160||||4"
msgid "Hi!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "161||||4"
msgid "Hi!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "162||||4"
msgid "Wow, such high energy!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "163||||4"
msgid "I'm glad to see your smiling faces here for\r\nthe Ono Michio-kun talk show! Thanks for coming!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "164||||4"
msgid "Yayyy!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "165||||4"
msgid "Yayyy!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "166||||4"
msgid "Yayyy!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "167||||4"
msgid "Yayyy!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "168||||4"
msgid "Hey, you didn't mention this talk show thing earlier."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "169||||4"
msgid "Hmhm? I could've sworn I told you.\r\nBut hey, look how excited the kids are!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "170||||4"
msgid "You can't be serious. I have no idea\r\nhow Ono Michio-kun is supposed to talk."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "171||||4"
msgid "It'll be fine! Just make something up\r\nif you don't know the answer. You can do it!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "172||||4"
msgid "Well, I'm out of here!\r\nGood luck with the talk show!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "173||||4"
msgid "Dammit... I won't forget this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "174||||4"
msgid "Here's the one you've all been waiting for!\r\nThe pride and joy of this town, Ono Michio-kun!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "175||||4"
msgid "Michio-kun!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "176||||4"
msgid "Michio-kun!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "177||||4"
msgid "Michio-kun!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "178||||4"
msgid "Michio-kun!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "179||||4"
msgid "Hm... Nice to michi!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "180||||4"
msgid "Now everyone, let's see what kind of questions\r\nyou have for our beloved Ono Michio-kun!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "181||||4"
msgid "Who wants to go first?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "182||||4"
msgid "Me, pick me!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "183||||4"
msgid "Me, pick me!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "184||||4"
msgid "Me, pick me!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "185||||4"
msgid "Me, pick me!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "186||||4"
msgid "Let's see... You!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "187||||4"
msgid "Um, can I ask you anything?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "188||||4"
msgid "Of course. Show me what you got."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "189||||4"
msgid "Then, um... what's your favorite food, Michio-kun?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "190||||4"
msgid "That's an excellent question!\r\nI'm dying to know, too! Well, Michio-kun?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "191||||4"
msgid "My favorite food, huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "192||||4"
msgid "I love things I can enjoy with a nice cold sake.\r\nCucumber salad is my go-to drinking food."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "193||||4"
msgid "Cucumber... salad...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "194||||4"
msgid "M-Michio-kun, you have such a refined palate."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "195||||4"
msgid "Shoot, I messed up.\r\nThat was a lie! My real favorite is..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "196||||4"
msgid "I eat everything... but nothing satisfies\r\nme quite like a sexy woman."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "197||||4"
msgid "Just kidding."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "198||||4"
msgid "Sexy...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "199||||4"
msgid "M-Michio-kun!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "200||||4"
msgid "Shoot, I messed up.\r\nThat was a joke! My real favorite is..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "201||||4"
msgid "Onomichi ramen-michi!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "202||||4"
msgid "Yayyy, I knew that was gonna be it!\r\nI can't get enough Onomichi ramen!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "203||||4"
msgid "What an answer!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "204||||4"
msgid "Yeah."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "205||||4"
msgid "All right... who wants to be next?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "206||||4"
msgid "Me! Please, pick me!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "207||||4"
msgid "Me! Please, pick me!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "208||||4"
msgid "Me! Please, pick me!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "209||||4"
msgid "Me! Please, pick me!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "210||||4"
msgid "Okay, you over there!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "211||||4"
msgid "Um... Someday, I hope I can get\r\nmarried to you, Michio-kun!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "212||||4"
msgid "Awww yeah!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "213||||4"
msgid "Awww yeah!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "214||||4"
msgid "Awww yeah!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "215||||4"
msgid "Michio-kun... Do you have a girlfriend?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "216||||4"
msgid "Ah, a young lady caught in the throes of love!\r\nWhat's your answer, Michio-kun?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "217||||4"
msgid "She wants to know if I'm dating anyone...\r\nThis is awkward. What should I say...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "218||||4"
msgid "I'm not involved with anyone right now...\r\nbut there was someone I set my heart on long ago."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "219||||4"
msgid "I don't think I'll ever see her again."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "220||||4"
msgid "If only I had been a little smarter back then...\r\nMaybe things would have been different."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "221||||4"
msgid "Every now and again, I regret that day.\r\nLife doesn't give you do-overs, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "222||||4"
msgid "U-Um..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "223||||4"
msgid "M-Michio-kun!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "224||||4"
msgid "Huh? Sh-Shoot, I messed up.\r\nWhat was it...? Oh yeah, I remember now!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "225||||4"
msgid "I'm the purest mascot in town.\r\nLove would only tarnish my sparkly clean image."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "226||||4"
msgid "From the day of my birth... I've remained a virgin."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "227||||4"
msgid "Virgin...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "228||||4"
msgid "M-Michio-kun!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "229||||4"
msgid "Huh? Sh-Shoot, I messed up.\r\nThat was just a joke, kiddos!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "230||||4"
msgid "What was it...? Oh yeah, I remember now!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "231||||4"
msgid "Oh no!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "232||||4"
msgid "Ah! There's Ono Michio-kun's trademark \"oh no\"!\r\nThings have really gone sour for this orange!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "237||||4"
msgid "Oh no!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "238||||4"
msgid "Oh no!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "239||||4"
msgid "Oh no!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "241||||4"
msgid "I dodged a bullet there."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "242||||4"
msgid "Okay! On to our next question."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "243||||4"
msgid "Hey! Shut the hell up!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "244||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "245||||4"
msgid "What in the...? Who are you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "246||||4"
msgid "Yer way too freakin' loud! I've had enough o'\r\nall these kids screamin' n' laughin' over here!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "247||||4"
msgid "This place's ours, y'know.\r\nWe didn't say ya could hang 'round here!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "248||||4"
msgid "So scary..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "249||||4"
msgid "Who are these guys...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "250||||4"
msgid "I'm so scared..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "252||||4"
msgid "Can't you see you're scaring the children?\r\nThat's enough!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "253||||4"
msgid "Little shits.\r\nY'wanna see somethin' real scary, huh!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "257||||4"
msgid "Somebody help..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "258||||4"
msgid "Hey."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "259||||4"
msgid "Huh? Y'lookin' fer trouble?\r\nStay outta this, mascot."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "260||||4"
msgid "Is that ramen on yer head?\r\nLame shit like that ain't ever gonna be cool!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "261||||4"
msgid "I can't disagree with you there. But making kids\r\ncry for no damn reason is far lamer than my hat."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "262||||4"
msgid "Huh? What was 'at?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "263||||4"
msgid "Is this dopey shit gonna fight us?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "264||||4"
msgid "I might be dopey... but even dopes know\r\nwhen to take out the trash. Let's do this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "265||||4"
msgid "Yer funny, guy.\r\nC'mon! Let's wreck this mascot fuck!"
